==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Penetrating
<hw>Pen"e*tra`ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Having the power of entering, piercing, or pervading; sharp;
subtile; penetrative; <as>as, a <ex>penetrating</ex>
odor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Acute; discerning; sagacious; quick to discover;
<as>as, a <ex>penetrating</ex> mind</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Penetratingly</ent>⟦br⟧
